{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b8b8602a7d","title":"毛泽东转发中南军区关于从民主检查转入清查贪污的指示的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"42fba9a055","index":0,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":27,"articleId":"b8b8602a7d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ce3eb49b34","type":"title","text":"毛泽东转发中南军区关于从民主检查转入清查贪污的指示的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b8b8602a7d"},{"id":"f942ea1e2e","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b8b8602a7d"},{"id":"fe73ace602","type":"appellation","text":"各大军区，志愿军：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b8b8602a7d"},{"id":"f80d15da9c","type":"paragraph","text":"中南军区一月二十五日的文件很好，发给你们参考。中南三反动手较迟，故对民主检查和反中小贪污两个阶段尚未做完的单位，必须做完，方能进入打老虎的第三阶段。各大军区和志愿军也须如此。但一切已做完第一第二阶段任务的，就应立即重组队伍，打老虎。但全军一切落后单位至迟均须于二月十日或十五日进入打虎阶级。中南文件所举七条寻找大老虎的嫌疑事踪，军事系统和地方系统都适用。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b8b8602a7d"},{"id":"b8209d397b","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东一月二十七日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b8b8602a7d"}],"page":{"id":"bc691caa46","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b8b8602a7d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}